body:
I just realized that this will fail on the Android tests since we've currently disabled `TF_LoadSessionFromSavedModel` in Android (since it pulls it a bit too many dependencies right now).
I'll make a change to `c_api.h` so that the symbol will exist, even if the call will fail on Android.

So no changes needed in this PR for that, but just a heads up.
